# grep -E '(auth.*|authpriv.*|daemon.*)' /etc/rsyslog.conf
# Don't log private authentication messages!
*.info;mail.none;authpriv.none;cron.none                /var/log/messages
# The authpriv file has restricted access.
authpriv.*                                              /var/log/secure
daemon.* /var/log/secure
auth.* /var/log/secure

[root@rhel8baseline ~]# ls -l /etc/cron.daily/
total 8
-rwxr-xr-x. 1 root root 189 Jan  4  2018 logrotate
-rwxr-xr-x. 1 root root 122 Dec  6 11:21 V230263

[root@rhel8baseline temp.admin]# grep -E '(\/usr\/sbin\/(audit|au|rsys))' /etc/aide.conf
/usr/sbin/auditctl p+i+n+u+g+s+b+acl+xattrs+sha512
/usr/sbin/auditd p+i+n+u+g+s+b+acl+xattrs+sha512
/usr/sbin/ausearch p+i+n+u+g+s+b+acl+xattrs+sha512
/usr/sbin/aureport p+i+n+u+g+s+b+acl+xattrs+sha512
/usr/sbin/autrace p+i+n+u+g+s+b+acl+xattrs+sha512
/usr/sbin/augenrules p+i+n+u+g+s+b+acl+xattrs+sha512
/usr/sbin/rsyslogd p+i+n+u+g+s+b+acl+xattrs+sha512
[root@rhel8baseline temp.admin]#

# grep @@ /etc/rsyslog.conf /etc/rsyslog.d/*.conf
/etc/rsyslog.conf:# Per CCE-80863-4: Set *.* @@logcollector in /etc/rsyslog.conf
/etc/rsyslog.conf:*.* @@logcollector
# dnf list installed | grep -i splunk
splunkforwarder.x86_64                        9.1.2-b6b9c8185839                          @@commandline
#

# grep -i '$DefaultNetstreamDriver' /etc/rsyslog.conf /etc/rsyslog.d/*.conf
/etc/rsyslog.d/encrypt.conf:$DefaultNetstreamDriver gtls
# grep -i '$ActionSendStreamDriverMode' /etc/rsyslog.conf /etc/rsyslog.d/*.conf
/etc/rsyslog.d/encrypt.conf:$ActionSendStreamDriverMode 1
# dnf list installed | grep -i splunk
splunkforwarder.x86_64                        9.1.2-b6b9c8185839                          @@commandline
#

# grep -i '$ActionSendStreamDriverAuthMode' /etc/rsyslog.conf /etc/rsyslog.d/*.conf
/etc/rsyslog.d/stream_driver_auth.conf:$ActionSendStreamDriverAuthMode x509/name
# dnf list installed | grep -i splunk
splunkforwarder.x86_64                        9.1.2-b6b9c8185839                          @@commandline
#

[root@rhel8baseline ~]# grep -E "[+]?acl" /etc/aide.conf
#acl:           Access Control Lists
#R:             p+i+n+u+g+s+m+c+acl+selinux+xattrs+md5
#L:             p+i+n+u+g+acl+selinux+xattrs
#>:             Growing logfile p+u+g+i+n+S+acl+selinux+xattrs
ALLXTRAHASHES = sha1+rmd160+sha256+sha512+tiger+xattrs+acl
EVERYTHING = R+ALLXTRAHASHES+acl+xattrs
NORMAL = p+i+n+u+g+s+m+c+acl+selinux+xattrs+sha512
DIR = p+i+n+u+g+acl+selinux+xattrs
PERMS = p+u+g+acl+selinux+xattrs
LOG = p+u+g+n+S+acl+selinux+xattrs
CONTENT = sha512+ftype+acl+xattrs
CONTENT_EX = sha512+ftype+p+u+g+n+acl+selinux+xattrs
DATAONLY = p+n+u+g+s+acl+selinux+xattrs+sha512
/usr/sbin/auditctl p+i+n+u+g+s+b+acl+xattrs+sha512
/usr/sbin/auditd p+i+n+u+g+s+b+acl+xattrs+sha512
/usr/sbin/ausearch p+i+n+u+g+s+b+acl+xattrs+sha512
/usr/sbin/aureport p+i+n+u+g+s+b+acl+xattrs+sha512
/usr/sbin/autrace p+i+n+u+g+s+b+acl+xattrs+sha512
/usr/sbin/augenrules p+i+n+u+g+s+b+acl+xattrs+sha512
/usr/sbin/rsyslogd p+i+n+u+g+s+b+acl+xattrs+sha512
/usr/bin/aulast p+i+n+u+g+s+b+acl+xattrs+sha512
/usr/bin/aulastlog p+i+n+u+g+s+b+acl+xattrs+sha512
/usr/bin/ausyscall p+i+n+u+g+s+b+acl+xattrs+sha512
/usr/bin/auvirt p+i+n+u+g+s+b+acl+xattrs+sha512
/usr/bin/rsyslog-recover-qi.pl p+i+n+u+g+s+b+acl+xattrs+sha512
